					{"course_id":26443,"nonce":"1ce0a6e274","id":35791,"title":"CO \u2013 Mock Exam 19","content":"","questions":[{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35792,"title":"Vous allez entendre des conversations entre deux personnes. Indiquez \u00e0 quel dessin correspond chaque conversation.<br><br><iframe src=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1U9JL6JwBpfmUq03JPKN3umVt8Cx2FvvK\/preview\" width=\"340\" height=\"60\" allow=\"autoplay\"><\/iframe><br><img src=\"https:\/\/tefcanada.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/co-19-1-min.png\" \/>","type":"single_choice","point":1,"explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Bonjour, je voudrais enregistrer ma valise.\n \u2014 Bien s\u00fbr, votre vol est \u00e0 quelle destination ?\n \u2014 Pour Montr\u00e9al \u00e0 14 heures 30.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"A","value":"552e098d","is_true":"","uid":12238},{"title":"B","value":"6d352451","is_true":"","uid":12239},{"title":"C","value":"3e66727d","is_true":"yes","uid":12240},{"title":"D","value":"fa284c33","is_true":"","uid":12241}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35793,"title":"Indiquez \u00e0 quel dessin correspond chaque conversation.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/tefcanada.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/co-19-2-min.png\" \/>","type":"single_choice","point":1,"explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Bonjour, qu'est-ce qui vous am\u00e8ne aujourd'hui ?\n \u2014 J'ai mal \u00e0 la gorge depuis 3 jours.\n \u2014 D'accord, je vais vous examiner.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"A","value":"a7a7ecb7","is_true":"","uid":12242},{"title":"B","value":"ad923610","is_true":"yes","uid":12243},{"title":"C","value":"43ab5d42","is_true":"","uid":12244},{"title":"D","value":"e66ee574","is_true":"","uid":12245}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35794,"title":"Indiquez \u00e0 quel dessin correspond chaque conversation.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/tefcanada.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/co-19-3-min.png\" \/>","type":"single_choice","point":1,"explanati