5},{"title":"Le retard du vol AF352.","value":"7e090ed8","is_true":"yes","uid":12256},{"title":"Un changement de porte d'embarquement.","value":"a0425916","is_true":"","uid":12257}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35797,"title":"D&#8217;apr\u00e8s ce message, cette r\u00e9duction concerne","type":"single_choice","point":1,"content":"<p>(Annonce 2)<\/p>\n","explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Chers clients, aujourd'hui seulement, b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiez d'une r\u00e9duction exceptionnelle de 20 % sur tous les produits Lifray. Profitez-en avant la fermeture du magasin ce soir.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"Tous les articles du magasin.","value":"843ad31a","is_true":"","uid":12258},{"title":"Les produits frais.","value":"38eb9adb","is_true":"yes","uid":12259},{"title":"Les produits en promotion.","value":"53df11fd","is_true":"","uid":12260},{"title":"Les articles m\u00e9nagers.","value":"fc1f4604","is_true":"","uid":12261}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35798,"title":"Ce message informe que ce train","type":"single_choice","point":1,"content":"<p>(Annonce 3)<\/p>\n","explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Le train en provenance de Lyon et \u00e0 destination de Marseille partira du quai num\u00e9ro 5 dans 10 minutes. Les passagers sont pri\u00e9s de se rendre sur le quai d\u00e8s maintenant.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"Part bient\u00f4t pour Marseille.","value":"79d1130c","is_true":"yes","uid":12262},{"title":"A \u00e9t\u00e9 annul\u00e9.","value":"d5089298","is_true":"","uid":12263},{"title":"A chang\u00e9 de quai.","value":"dae0c750","is_true":"","uid":12264},{"title":"Est arriv\u00e9 en retard.","value":"87ceb111","is_true":"","uid":12265}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35799,"title":"Ce message indique que la s\u00e9ance","type":"single_choice","point":1,"content":"<p>(Annonce 4)<\/p>\n","explanation":"Transcription - \n\n La s\u00e9ance du film Le Grand Voyage, pr\u00e9vue \u00e0 dix-huit heures 30, d\u00e9butera dans quelques minutes. Les spectateurs sont pri\u00e9s de rejoindre la salle d\u00e8s maintenant.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"A \u00e9t\u00e9 annul\u00e9e.","value":"bdae7199","is_true":"","uid":12266},{"title":"Va bient\u00f4t commencer.","value":"7081f237","is_true":"yes","uid":12267},{"title":"A \u00e9t\u00e9 report\u00e9e.","value":"81858b2e","is_true":"","uid":12268},{"title":"Est compl\u00e8te.","value":"d935ff3b","is_true":"","uid":12269}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35800,"title":"La personne appelle pour&#8230;","type":"single_choice","point":1,"content":"<p>Vous allez entendre UNE fois de ces six messages. <\/p>\n<p>\u00c9coutez et indiquez pourquoi la personne appelle.<\/p>\n","explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Bonjour, j'ai vu votre publicit\u00e9 pour un atelier de d\u00e9gustation. Je suis int\u00e9ress\u00e9, mais je voudrais plus de renseignements. Pourriez-vous me rappeler au cinquante-cinq 81 soixante-neuf soixante-quinze vingt-trois ? Merci beaucoup.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"donner des pr\u00e9cisions.","value":"15dc01a1","is_true":"","uid":12270},{"title":"promouvoir un article.","value":"17bd7641","is_true":"","uid":12271},{"title":"obtenir des informations.","value":"221b307a","is_true":"yes","uid":12272},{"title":"confirmer sa participation.","value":"20e5638f","is_true":"","uid":12273}]},{"object":{"object_type":"question"},"id":35801,"title":"La personne appelle pour&#8230;","type":"single_choice","point":1,"content":"<p>(Message 2)<\/p>\n","explanation":"Transcription - \n\n Salut Williams, j'esp\u00e8re que tu vas bien. Mon ordinateur est encore en panne, le probl\u00e8me n'est pas r\u00e9gl\u00e9. Est-ce que tu pourrais regarder une derni\u00e8re fois ? Bon, je te rappelle, bisous.","has_explanation":true,"options":[{"title":"proposer de l'aide.","value":"238547ad","is_true":"","uid":12274},{"title":"vendre un produit.","value":"72be2c0b","is_true":"","uid":12275},{"title":"inv